ry.html |title=Trial of the Century? |website=Law.umkc.edu |date=1999-01-28 |accessdate=2017-03-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100308144315/http://www.law.umkc.edu/faculty/projects/ftrials/century.html |archivedate=2010-03-08 |df= }}</ref> *[[Gloria Vanderbilt]] custody trial (1934)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://law.jrank.org/pages/2927/Gloria-Vanderbilt-Custody-Trial-1934--Trial-Century.html|title=Gloria Vanderbilt Custody Trial: 1934 - "trial Of The Century"|website=Law.jrank.org|accessdate=15 March 2017}}</ref> *[[Lindbergh kidnapping]] trial (1935)<ref>{{cite web |author=Doug Linder |url=http://www.law.umkc.edu/faculty/projects/ftrials/Hauptmann/AccountHauptmann.html |title=An Account of the Trial of Richard Hauptmann |website=Law.umkc.edu |date= |accessdate=2017-03-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090709013003/http://www.law.umkc.edu/faculty/projects/ftrials/Hauptmann/AccountHauptmann.html |archivedate=2009-07-09 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title = Crimes and Trials of the Century [2 volumes]|url = https://books.google.com/books?id=FPRslbPnMjwC|publisher = ABC-CLIO|date = 2007-10-30|isbn = 9781573569736|language = en|first = Frankie Y. Bailey|last = Ph.D|first2 = Steven Chermak|last2 = Ph.D|page = 167}}</ref> *[[Nuremberg trials]] (1945–1946) <ref name=nuremberg>{{cite news |first=Joseph |last=Kanon |authorlink=Joseph Kanon |coauthors= |title=The Real Trial of the Century |url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E01E2D81F3BF93AA35755C0A9649C8B63 |quote= |newspaper=[[The New York Times]] |date=June 9, 2002 |accessdate=2008-06-13}}</ref><ref name=nuremberg2>{{cite web |url=http://www.law.case.edu/saddamtrial/entry.asp?entry_id=14 |title=Saddam on Trial: Understanding and Debating the Iraqi High Tribunal 229 |year=2006 |accessdate=November 13, 2012 |quote= |publisher=[[Case Western Reserve University]] |author1=Michael P. Scharf |author2=Gregory S. McNeal |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.or